name: Latitude Template
format:
<template>
      <iframe  
              id="latitudeIframe"
              class="responsive-iframe"
              style="overflow:hidden; margin:auto; border:0px solid green;"></iframe>
    </template>
<script>
this.$socket.on('msg-input:' + this.id, function(msg) {
var x = document.getElementById('latitudeIframe');
x.setAttribute('src', msg.payload);
})
</script>
